---
title: "Reflection on the Use of GenAI"
---

## How I used GenAI

I used ChatGPT to help me:
- Structure my Quarto website
- Write clean Markdown
- Organize my portfolio pages

## Benefits

GenAI helped me quickly:
- Convert ideas into formatted web pages
- Debug Quarto and GitHub issues
- Improve clarity of writing

## Challenges

Sometimes the output needed:
- Verification
- Adjustments for technical accuracy

## Future use

I will continue using GenAI for:
- Coding
- Data analysis
- Technical writing
- System design
